<pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>To beget; to engender.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gender</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Gender
<hw>Gen"der</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To copulate; to breed.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Genderless</ent>⟦br⟧
